    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered in a climate-controlled garage and the paint is just glowing. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. You really won\u2019t find another one this clean. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
      "price": 44500.0,
