    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of the S54-powered era, maintained to an exacting standard. The high-strung 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS for immediate throttle response and a linear power band. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the rod bearings have been proactively serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate chassis fatigue. The Getrag manual gearbox provides precise engagement, feeding a variable M-differential lock that ensures maximum traction. Every seal is tight, the cooling system has been refreshed, and the suspension retains its factory-intended kinematics. This is a turn-key example for a collector who values mechanical perfection and performance purity.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
